parameters:
\nw[\N[3]]\N[1] seems to be in a good mood. She needs to stay
focused, or it could be dangerous, you know?

\nw[\N[1]]Even if you say that, my dream is finally coming
true.

\nw[\N[1]]If we get paid for this job, we can move our base.
It would be strange not to be happy about it.

\nw[\N[1]]It may not be possible in this country, but if we
go to the neighboring Misura country, the three of
us can get married. That's why I've been working
so hard all this time.

\nw[\N[3]]It would be fine if \N[1] and \N[21] got married,
right? After all, I am their parent, so they don't
have to be so fixated on it...

\nw[\N[1]]No! \N[3] is family! She has always taken care of
me and \N[21], who lost our family!

\nw[\N[1]]I want to be together with \N[3] and \N[21] forever!
I want proof of that.

\nw[\N[21]]Oh, yeah. We already discussed and decided on it
before.

\nw[\N[3]]I understand. But please don't push yourself too
hard.
\nw[\N[1]]Don't worry, this job isn't that dangerous.

\nw[\N[1]]Oh, it's about time. \N[3], are you okay with the
time?
\nw[\N[3]]My work is a little further ahead.
